{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Navigation directive (ナビゲーションディレクティブ)","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Glossary/Navigation_directive","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"\n<ol>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary\">用語集</a>\n  <ol>\n   <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/CSP\">CSP</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Fetch_directive\">フェッチディレクティブ</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Document_directive\">文書ディレクティブ</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Reporting_directive\">報告ディレクティブ</a></li>\n  </ol>\n </li>\n</ol>\n","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"learn_more","title":"関連項目","isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/CSP\">CSP</a> のナビゲーションディレクティブ</strong>は <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Security-Policy\"><code>Content-Security-Policy</code></a> ヘッダーで使用され、たとえば、ユーザーがどの場所に移動したり、フォームを送信したりすることができるかを管理します。</p>\n\n<p>ナビゲーションディレクティブは <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Security-Policy/default-src\"><code>default-src</code></a> ディレクティブで代替されません。</p>\n\n<p>完全な一覧は<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Security-Policy#navigation_directives\">ナビゲーションディレクティブ</a>を参照してください。</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect1\">\n\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/CSP/#directives-navigation\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">https://www.w3.org/TR/CSP/#directives-navigation</a></li>\n <li>他の種類のディレクティブ:\n  <ul>\n   <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Fetch_directive\">フェッチディレクティブ</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Document_directive\">文書ディレクティブ</a></li>\n   <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Glossary/Reporting_directive\">報告ディレクティブ</a></li>\n   <li><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Security-Policy/block-all-mixed-content\">block-all-mixed-content</a></code></li>\n   <li><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Security-Policy/upgrade-insecure-requests\">upgrade-insecure-requests</a></code></li>\n   <li><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Security-Policy/require-sri-for\">require-sri-for</a></code></li>\n   <li><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Security-Policy/trusted-types\">trusted-types</a></code></li>\n  </ul>\n </li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Content-Security-Policy\"><code>Content-Security-Policy</code></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"関連項目","id":"learn_more"}],"summary":"CSP のナビゲーションディレクティブは Content-Security-Policy ヘッダーで使用され、たとえば、ユーザーがどの場所に移動したり、フォームを送信したりすることができるかを管理します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Navigation directive","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Directive de navigation","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Navigation directive","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/glossary/navigation_directive","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/glossary/navigation_directive/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary","title":"MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Glossary/Navigation_directive","title":"Navigation directive (ナビゲーションディレクティブ)"}],"pageTitle":"Navigation directive (ナビゲーションディレクティブ) - MDN Web Docs 用語集: ウェブ関連用語の定義 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}